{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01DTkzKQYvksiDHjwr4oyxEN","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## Migration Summary\n\n**Frameworks:** Spring Boot 3.x + JoinFaces JSF -> Quarkus 3.8.4\n**Outcome:** Success - all 9 smoke tests passing\n\n### High-level actions:\n1. Replaced all Spring Boot dependencies with Quarkus equivalents in pom.xml\n2. Converted Spring Data JPA repository to Panache repository\n3. Migrated Spring service bean to CDI ApplicationScoped bean\n4. Replaced JSF managed bean controller with JAX-RS REST resource\n5. Updated application.properties from Spring to Quarkus format\n6. Updated Dockerfile to build and run Quarkus fast-jar\n7. Removed Spring-specific files (Application.java, ServletInitializer, config classes)\n8. Added validation exception mapper for proper HTTP 400 responses\n\n### File Tree\n\n```\nModified:\n- pom.xml: Replaced Spring Boot/JoinFaces dependencies with Quarkus (resteasy-reactive-jackson, hibernate-orm-panache, jdbc-h2, hibernate-validator, arc)\n- src/main/resources/application.properties: Migrated Spring config to Quarkus config format\n- src/main/java/.../entity/Contact.java: Extended PanacheEntity instead of manual @Id/@GeneratedValue\n- src/main/java/.../repo/ContactRepository.java: Converted from Spring Data JpaRepository to Panache PanacheRepository\n- src/main/java/.../service/ContactService.java: Converted from Spring @Service to CDI @ApplicationScoped, Panache API\n- src/main/java/.../web/ContactController.java: Rewrote from JSF managed bean to JAX-RS REST resource\n- Dockerfile: Changed CMD from spring-boot:run to java -jar quarkus-run.jar, added build step\n\nAdded:\n- src/main/java/.../web/ValidationExceptionMapper.java: Maps validation errors to HTTP 400 JSON responses\n- smoke.py: 9 smoke tests for CRUD operations via REST API\n- CHANGELOG.md: Complete migration documentation\n\nRemoved:\n- src/main/java/.../Application.java: Spring Boot main class (not needed in Quarkus)\n- src/main/java/.../ServletInitializer.java: Spring WAR initializer (not needed)\n- src/main/java/.../config/JsfConfig.java: JSF servlet registration (not needed)\n- src/main/java/.../config/SpringConfig.java: Spring component scan (not needed)\n```\n\n### Error Handling\n- **No critical errors encountered** during the migration\n- Maven build succeeded on first attempt\n- Quarkus application started successfully in 2.3 seconds\n- All 9 smoke tests passed on first run (both from host and inside container)"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":347,"cache_read_input_tokens":108270,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":347,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":656},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"3d45ec05-ee5c-4446-866d-56d1c15c4587","uuid":"58ee0941-ef2b-4d34-96da-b3b3a59d6775"}
